    "image_with_text_t6KzFw": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_CcwiLn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/leesdonuts.ca/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/leesdonuts.ca/\">Johnny (Lee's Donuts)</a></p><p>If you’ve ever strolled past a <a href=\"https://www.leesdonuts.ca/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lee’s Donuts</span></a> shop and caught sight of a cheerful, frosting-covered face waving you in, you’ve already met Johnny Glaze — their sugary-smooth mascot with a heart as warm as a fresh batch of <a href=\"https://www.leesdonuts.ca/donut-menu\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">honey dip donuts</span></a>. With his signature glazed smile and a personality that’s 100% sweet (but not overly sweet), Johnny isn’t just a donut — he’s the embodiment of everything Lee’s Donuts stands for: fresh and friendly with a whole lot of flavor. Whether he’s popping up at <a href=\"https://www.leesdonuts.ca/events\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">community events</span></a> or starring in their latest <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/leesdonuts.ca/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">social posts</span></a>, Johnny brings a sprinkle of warmth and fun to your daily donut run. </p><p>Recently, Johnny started working at <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/pages/store-locator\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Plenty Metrotown</span></a> where he’s trading glaze for gaze as a retail associate. While his roots are in rising dough, Johnny’s heart has always been set on rising trends. With his eye for style and naturally sweet demeanor, he’s finding fresh ways to express himself — pairing cuffed denim with donut-box pastels and serving looks as fresh as his old bakery batches. Whether helping guests find the perfect fit or mixing textures like a pro, Johnny’s proving that fashion and frosting make a surprisingly chic combo.</p><p>We spent the morning with Johnny to hear more about his experience as the newest employee at Metrotown, read below.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_CcwiLn"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_6362-Enhanced-NR.jpg",
