    "image_with_text_FAfVaW": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_tfc8jA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Q: </strong>As a retail associate, how do you sprinkle joy into customer interactions? </p><p><strong>A:</strong> Let’s just say, I’ve got a silent-but-sweet approach with customers. I’m a master at the art of communication. Actually, a lot of people don’t know this, but I’ve got my Masters of Arts in Communication. My final thesis was on how joy can be spread through dance moves, enthusiastic high-fives and free donuts. </p><p><strong>Q:</strong> If you could stock one donut-inspired item in Plenty’s inventory, what would it be? </p><p><strong>A: </strong>Hmm, that’s a good one. I’d say round donut-shaped tote bags. Perfect for carrying home fresh treats from our pop-up! I express everything through action and not words so I think fashion should speak for itself too. Plus, who doesn't need more circular accessories in their life? </p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
